data.description:
Opportunity knocks! This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a generous 2-car garage is your chance to transform a house into your perfect home. Featuring brand new carpeting, fresh interior paint, and enclosed patio this property offers a solid foundation for your personal touch and creativity.
Bring your vision to life in the spacious living and dining areas, where the neutral palette provides a canvas ready for your unique style. The kitchen awaits your design flair, and with a little TLC, it can become a culinary haven.
Conveniently located near schools, parks, and amenities, this charming abode presents an exceptional opportunity to create a space that truly feels like home. Don't miss out on this chance to turn potential into reality—schedule your showing today!
